    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Product Designer",
    "long_instructions": "## Product Designer\r\n\r\nProduct designers focus on the user experience (UX/UI), making sure technology is easy to use, aesthetically appealing, and functional. They work with software and hardware teams to bridge the gap between design and technology.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * How their role contributes to building your innovation\r\n   * The challenges they face in designing, developing, or refining innovations\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
    "aichat_settings": {
